ary 25, 2014, our board of directors approved a 42 cent per share dividend, payable", "bbox": [96.6, 690.6, 1154.9, 713.7]}, {"text": "March 10, 2014 to stockholders of record at the close of business on February 19, 2014.", "bbox": [96.6, 715.7, 829.5, 738.7]}, {"text": "Dividends on our common stock are limited to our legally available funds.", "bbox": [96.6, 759.4, 717.3, 782.5]}, {"text": "Issuer Purchases of Equity Securities", "bbox": [96.6, 813.6, 425.9, 836.7]}, {"text": "The following table sets forth a summary of our purchases during the quarter ended December 31, 2013, of equity securities", "bbox": [96.6, 849.0, 1136.3, 872.1]}, {"text": "that are registered by MPC pursuant to Section 12 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended:", "bbox": [96.6, 874.0, 959.2, 897.1]}, {"text": "Period", "bbox": [102.8, 1046.7, 157.3, 1069.7]}, {"text": "Total Number", "bbox": [388.8, 1005.0, 504.8, 1028.1]}, {"text": "of Shares", "bbox": [407.7, 1025.8, 485.9, 1048.9]}, {"text": "Purchased(a)", "bbox": [396.4, 1043.7, 497.1, 1069.7]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [579.0, 1005.0, 648.1, 1028.1]}, {"text": "Price Paid", "bbox": [571.0, 1025.8, 656.1, 1048.9]}, {"text": "per Share(b)", "bbox": [566.0, 1043.7, 661.1, 1069.7]}, {"text": "Total Number of", "bbox": [741.2, 963.3, 879.8, 986.4]}, {"text": "Shares Purchased as", "bbox": [726.1, 984.1, 895.1, 1007.2]}, {"text": "Part of Publicly", "bbox": [745.1, 1005.0, 876.0, 1028.1]}, {"text": "Announced Plans", "bbox": [737.3, 1025.8, 883.8, 1048.9]}, {"text": "or Programs", "bbox": [759.3, 1046.7, 861.8, 1069.7]}, {"text": "Maximum Dollar", "bbox": [965.1, 963.3, 1110.4, 986.4]}, {"text": "Value of Shares that", "bbox": [954.1, 984.1, 1121.4, 1007.2]}, {"text": "May Yet Be Purchased", "bbox": [942.8, 1005.0, 1132.7, 1028.1]}, {"text": "Under the Plans", "bbox": [971.2, 1025.8, 1104.4, 1048.9]}, {"text": "or Programs(c)", "bbox": [979.0, 1043.7, 1096.6, 1069.7]}, {"text": "10/01/13-10/31/13", "bbox": [102.8, 1076.1, 2