hare repurchase authorizations and for shares", "bbox": [171.6, 1244.1, 1121.5, 1262.6]}, {"text": "tendered to us in satisfaction of employee tax withholding obligations upon the vesting of restricted stock granted under our stock plans. The", "bbox": [171.6, 1264.1, 1114.8, 1282.6]}, {"text": "weighted average price includes commissions paid to brokers on shares purchased under our share repurchase authorizations.", "bbox": [171.6, 1284.2, 1007.2, 1302.6]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [134.1, 1301.8, 148.8, 1313.8]}, {"text": "On February 1, 2012, we announced that our board of directors authorized a share repurchase plan, enabling us to purchase up to $2.0 billion of our", "bbox": [171.6, 1304.2, 1161.0, 1322.6]}, {"text": "common stock over a two-year period to expire on January 31, 2014. On January 30, 2013, we announced that our board of directors approved an", "bbox": [171.6, 1324.2, 1147.5, 1342.6]}, {"text": "additional $2.0 billion share repurchase authorization to expire on December 31, 2014. On September 26, 2013, we announced that our board of", "bbox": [171.6, 1344.2, 1137.4, 1362.6]}, {"text": "directors approved an additional $2.0 billion share repurchase authorization through September 30, 2015. As indicated from these three", "bbox": [171.6, 1364.2, 1078.0, 1382.6]}, {"text": "announcements, our board of directors approved $6.0 billion in total share repurchase authorizations since January 1, 2012. As of December 31,", "bbox": [171.6, 1384.2, 1135.9, 1402.6]}, {"text": "2013, we have purchased a total of $4.14 billion of our common stock under these repurchase authorizations.", "bbox": [171.6, 1404.2, 903.5, 1422.7]}]}